{{Infobox software |name = Edraw Max |logo=Ed-logo.png |screenshot = Workflow-software.gif |caption = Edraw Max running on [[Windows 7]]. |developer = [[EdrawSoft]] |genre = Diagramming software |license = [[Proprietary software|Proprietary]] |website = {{url|http://www.edrawsoft.com}} |latest_release_version = 8 |latest_release_date = {{release date and age|2016|04|09}} |operating_system = [[Windows]], [[macOS]], [[Linux]] }}
'''Edraw Max''' is a 2D business technical diagramming software which help create flowcharts, organizational charts, mind map,<ref>{{cite web |title=Edraw Max is comprehensive mind mapping and planning tool|url=http://edraw-max.en.softonic.com|date=2011-03-14}}</ref> network diagrams, floor plans, workflow diagrams, business charts, and engineering diagrams. The current version, Edraw Max 8 was released on April 9, 2016 for Microsoft Windows, macOS, and Linux.
== Features == The current version, Edraw Max, is available in two editions: Free Viewer Version,<ref>{{cite web |title=Free Viewer for Edraw Files|url=http://www.edrawsoft.com/edrawviewer.php |date=2012-05-01}}</ref> Professional Editable Version. The latter has additional templates and examples for creating diagrams.
A free trial is available for 30 days. It is not possible to save Edraw files in the trial version.
Edraw Max gives users a Visio-like,<ref>{{cite web |title=Is Edraw a solid diagramming replacement for Visio?|url=http://www.techrepublic.com/blog/networking/review-is-edraw-a-solid-diagramming-replacement-for-visio/3371 |date=2010-09-16}}</ref> professional quality diagramming tool.
The interface uses a ribbon layout.
Edraw Max can generate organizational charts, Gantt charts and mind maps from data.<ref>{{cite web |title=Edraw Mind Map won the Spectacular award at CNET editor's rating|url=http://download.cnet.com/Edraw-Mind-Map/3000-18509_4-197599.html|date=2012-01-03}}</ref>
==File format== Edraw Max saves content in an xml file format. The .edx suffix is the default file format. The .edxz suffix is a compressed xml file format used for sharing.
